title: #92Noon! Russo/Leber/Gleeman/Florio
description: Some Timberwolves and NFC talk to get things started. Mike Russo joins over the Opal to discuss the Zucker trade and what the goal tending might look like the rest of the season. Ben Leber in studio, he digs deep on the psychology of playing under threat of trade. Aaron Gleeman checks in once again from Twins Training Camp in Florida. And the elite football mind of Mike Florio to finish things off.
